summary: Thoughts on the upcoming Nintendo Switch games?
question: Thoughts on the upcoming Nintendo Switch games?
answer:
There are so many that I like. There is a nice balance between new and returning IPs. The immediate release of Collection of Mana took me by pleasant surprise. Running up that is Banjo’s inclusion, since I did not know that Super Smash Bros. Ultimate was still being supported after this time. I am also surprised that Crypt of the Necromance_r and especially _Cadence of Hyrule are actually being on a Nintendo platform! I also am interested in Trackher, Dæmon X Machina, Hamsterdam, Astral Chain, Spiritfarer, Oninaki, The Dark Crystal, New Super Lucky’s Tale, Final Fantasy: Crystal Chronicles, Link’s Awakening, and, of course, Pokémon Sword and Shield.

If only I have a (1.0.0) Switch, myself!

Bowser - Super Mario Bros.
